   "source": [
    "# Variant comparison: perishable goods\n",
    "Test two variants, one without perishable goods ($\\beta=0$ and no $T_{max}$)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b8baee54",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Model m0 (Full)"
   ]
  },
